            <a
              href="/contatti"
              class="mt-7 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base md:text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-slate-100
                     underline underline-offset-4 decoration-pink-400/70 hover:decoration-pink-500"
            >
              Voglio un fix <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
